{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 61,
  "title": "第六十一章（謙德）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "大國者下流，"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下之交，"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下之牝。"
    },
    {
      "text": "牝常以靜勝牡，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以靜為下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故大國以下小國，則取小國，"
    },
    {
      "text": "小國以下大國，則取大國。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故或下以取，或下而取。"
    },
    {
      "text": "大國不過欲兼畜人，"
    },
    {
      "text": "小國不過欲入事人。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫兩者各得其所欲，大者宜為下。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治大國，當如居下流，不逆細微。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國，天下士民之所交會。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "牝者，陰類也。柔謙和而不昌也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "女所以能屈男，陰勝陽，以，安靜不先求之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "陰道以安靜為謙下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能謙下之，則常有之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此言國無大小，能持謙畜人，則無過失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "下者謂大國以下小國，小國以下大國，更以義相取。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國不失下，則兼併小國而牧畜之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使為臣僕。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國小國各欲得其所，大國又宜為謙下",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
